params.description:
Valid JSON containing [the array of objects](https://api-docs.deepseek.com/api/create-chat-completion), e.g. [{"role":"user","content":"Hello!"}, {"role": "assistant", "content": "Hi there! How can I help you today?"}]

`role` can be one of (**the roles should alternate**):

`system` - the message author role is system;

`user` - the message author role is user;

`assistant` - the message author role is assistant;

`tool` - the message author role is tool;

value.string:
export default async function run({ data }) {
    // data содержит массив с данными из Telegram
    const messageText = data["{{$15.data.update.message.text}}"];

    return {
        sendWelcome: messageText === '/start'
    };
}

